short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a dial button to phone numbers.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This chrome extension is developed by the Octavebytes to make outbound calls from the GoHighLevel contact page via Octavebytes's GoHighLevel CTI connector.

When the user clicks on the dial button, this extension passes the contact's phone number to Octavebytes's CTI connector to complete the outbound call.
